#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plain Bricks"
msgstr "Tavaline tellis"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simple bricks, while their appearance may vary they all behave the same way, "
"they get destroyed when hit by the ball and may contain a gift."
msgstr ""
"Kõige tavalisem tellis, mille välimus võib küll varieeruda, aga mis käitub "
"alati ühtmoodi: pihta saades hävib. Võib sisaldada kingitust."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Unbreakable Brick</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Purunematu tellis</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Unbreakable Brick</term>"
msgstr "<term>Purunematu tellis</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Never gets destroyed unless hit by a burning or unstoppable ball, or an "
"exploding brick next to it gets hit. These bricks do not need to be "
"destroyed to win the level."
msgstr ""
"Tellis, mis ei hävi kunagi, kui seda ei taba just põlev või peatumatu pall "
"või kui tabamust ei saa selle kõrval asuv plahvatav tellis. Nende telliste "
"hävitamine ei ole taseme võitmiseks vajalik."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Breakable Brick</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Purustatav tellis</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Breakable Brick</term>"
msgstr "<term>Purustatav tellis</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unbreakable bricks can be turned into breakable bricks using <link linkend="
"\"gift-magic-wand\">Magic Wand gift</link>."
msgstr ""
"Purunematuid telliseid saab muuta purustatavaks <link linkend=\"gift-magic-"
"wand\">võlukepi kingitusega</link>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Hidden Brick</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Peidetud tellis</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Hidden Brick</term>"
msgstr "<term>Peidetud tellis</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This brick is not initially shown to the player. When hit for the fist "
#| "time it becomes visible, and becomes a plain brick. If hit by a burning "
#| "ball, or an exploding brick next to it gets hit it gets destroyed as soon "
#| "as it appears. As long as it remains hidden it does not need to be "
#| "destroyed to get to the next level."
msgid ""
"This brick is not initially shown to the player. When hit for the first time "
"it becomes visible, and becomes a plain brick. If hit by a burning ball, or "
"an exploding brick next to it gets hit it gets destroyed as soon as it "
"appears. As long as it remains hidden it does not need to be destroyed to "
"get to the next level."
msgstr ""
"Seda tellist algul mängijale ei näidata. See ilmub nähtavale alles esimese "
"tabamuse järel ja muutub siis tavaliseks telliseks. Kui peidetud tellist "
"tabab põlev pall või tabamuse saab selle kõrval asuv plahvatav tellis, hävib "
"peidetud tellis kohe nähtavale ilmumisel. Kuni tellis on nähtamatu, ei ole "
"seda vaja järgmisele tasemele jõudmiseks hävitada."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Multiple Brick</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Mitmiktellis</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Multiple Brick</term>"
msgstr "<term>Mitmiktellis</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Needs to be hit three times before getting destroyed, unless hit by a "
"burning or unstoppable ball, or an exploding brick next to it gets destroyed."
msgstr ""
"Seda tellist tuleb tabada kolm korda, enne kui see hävib, kui seda ei taba "
"just põlev või peatumatu pall või kui tabamust ei saa selle kõrval asuv "
"plahvatav tellis."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Exploding Brick</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Plahvatav tellis</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Exploding Brick</term>"
msgstr "<term>Plahvatav tellis</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this brick gets hit also the bricks to the top, bottom, left and right "
"of it will get destroyed, regardless of their type."
msgstr ""
"Kui selline tellis saab tabamuse, hävivad ka selle kohal, all, vasakul ja "
"paremal asuvad tellised sõltumata oma tüübist."

