#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Sticky Bar Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Kleepuva lati kingitus</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After catching this gift, every time a ball touches the bar it remains "
"attached to it, allowing the player to fire again."
msgstr ""
"Kinnipüüdmisel muutub latt kleepuvaks, nii et pall seda tabades jääb lati "
"külge, mis võimaldab mängijal selle oma tahtmist mööda välja lasta."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>More Exploding Bricks Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Plahvatavate telliste paljundamise kingitus</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>More Exploding Bricks Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Plahvatavate telliste paljundamise kingitus</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Makes all bricks to the top, bottom, right, and left of exploding bricks "
"exploding bricks themselves. This also applies to hidden and unbreakable "
"bricks."
msgstr ""
"Muudab kõik plahvatavate telliste kohal ja all ning neist vasakul ja paremal "
"asuvad telliseid samuti plahvatavaks. See kehtib ka peidetud ja purunematute "
"telliste kohta."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Burning Ball Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Põleva palli kingitus</phrase>"

