#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:450
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Transforms all the balls in burning balls. When a burning ball hits a "
#| "brick also the bricks to the top, bottom, left and right of it get "
#| "destroyed. A burning ball destroys all types of bricks regardless of "
#| "their types."
msgid ""
