#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strateegia ja nõuanded"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If possible, it is usually a good idea to send the ball above the bricks, "
"doing so you will have a smaller chance of losing the ball. Sometimes you "
"need to first make a small hole in the layer of brick to accomplish this. "
"The smaller the hole, the smaller the chance the balls comes back down."
msgstr ""
"Kui võimalik, tasuks alati saata pall telliste kohale, sest nii on võimalus "
"seda kaotada väiksem. Mõnikord tuleb selleks kõigepealt tellisekihti avaus "
"tekitada. Mida väiksem avaus, seda väiksem ka võimalus, et pall kiiresti "
"tagasi tuleb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When catching the add ball gift it is wise to not fire it right away but to "
"keep in instead, in case the other balls are lost. It is also advisable to "
"not catch a sticky bar gift in such a case, as doing so would force you to "
"fire all balls."
msgstr ""
"Lisapalli kingituse saamisel on enamasti mõttekas seda kohe mitte välja "
"lasta, vaid jätta see vähemalt mõneks ajaks seisma, et selle abil vajaduse "
"korral kompenseerida teiste pallide kaotust. Samuti on soovitatav sellisel "
"juhul mitte kinni püüda kleepuva lati kingitust, sest see sunnib seejärel "
"kõik pallid välja laskma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When receiving a next level gift you may not want to catch it if you know "
"that there are add life gifts in the level."
msgstr ""
"Järgmise taseme kingituse puhul ei pruugi seda kinni püüda, kui tead, et "
"tasemel leidub ka lisaelude kingitusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In levels where there are a lot of hidden bricks there may be a way to win "
"the level without having to destroy most of them."
msgstr ""
"Tasemetel, kus leidub hulganisti peidetud telliseid, on päris mõttekas tase "
"võita neid võimalikult vähe hävitades."

